{"tid":1031106,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：六四舞台劇《5月35日》星級陣容編導 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-02-21T12:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T12:06:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"adb01048686edbfc82dc056f34aaf614d4929eef","tid":1031106,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:06:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190221/20617558\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190221%2F20617558&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD1JiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=44c3be0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190221%2F20617558&h=664ef834\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190221/20617558</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：六四舞台劇《5月35日》星級陣容編導 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190221/large/a1107a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190221%2Flarge%2Fa1107a.gif&h=dec8f288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《5月35日》將於5月底公演四場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年係六四屠城30周年，差不多每年都會以六四為主題創作舞台劇嘅「六四舞台」，今年將會上演一套名為《5月35日》嘅作品，編劇由《短暫的婚姻》編劇莊梅岩負責，由《香港式離婚》導演李鎮洲執導。<br />\n<br />\n5月35日就係6月4日。六四舞台喺fb為《5月35日》宣傳，話呢套劇係講述一對年邁夫婦嘅遭遇，兩人唯一兒子喺30年前「死於不自然」，至今真相仍然不明不白，二人決定要喺5月35日當天，堂堂正正去拜祭兒子，並擲地有聲拋下一句：「在不正常國家的陽光底下做正常的事也是不合法的。」<br />\n<br />\n《5月35日》將於5月底公演四場，票價由180元至320元，3月18日前可透過網上優先預留座位兼享折扣優惠，門票320元的優惠價為290元，<a href=\"http://有興趣嘅朋友可以上www.art-mate.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9C%89%E8%88%88%E8%B6%A3%E5%98%85%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8Awww.art-mate.net&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD1JiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=315a0cf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">有興趣嘅朋友可以上www.art-mate.net</a>訂票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：國籍風波引發改議規 民主派輪流抽擊梁君彥 (李八方)"}]}